OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy in the south
OL,6,Fwith patchy drizzle, plus coastal fog
OL,7,Fin the far southwest. Sunny spells
OL,8,Femerging in the north, though showers
OL,9,Faffecting northwest Scotland. Breezy
OL,10,Ffor all. Feeling humid in the south,
OL,11,Fbut fresher further north.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRather windy in the north
OL,14,Fwith further showers, heavy at times.
OL,15,FMostly dry with clear spells in the
OL,16,Fsouth, but low cloud lingering in the
OL,17,Fsouthwest. Cooler than last night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
